* Iron Raptor narrowed her optics at Tigerhawk back, she knew how to fight 
and she knew the signs of one to come as well!
She snarled and turned towards a separate computer screen, she slid a thin 
flap of metal back from her wrist and drew out a small cord attached to it. 
She then attached it to a small hole in the side of the screen and began to 
run the screen on her own internal power, it payed to have a reserve of 
energy just for tasks like this.*

" I'm not a kid!"

* Iron Raptor then jerked her head forward and a pair of online screen 
shades dropped from her brow and covered her optics, she then placed her 
hand over an information input hole. An information imputer (like the plug 
in for a pair of disc-man earphones.)slipped easily into the input station 
from the palm of her hand and she was soon browsing through her internal 
files.*

< It pays to be biologically engineared!>

* Iron Raptor twisted her hand to the left and smiled as it locked into the 
imputer, now she was going to rock!
A personal file caught her scanners and she soon brought it up on the 
computer screen, an image of a twelve pointed star appeared.
Iron Raptor smiled and said loud enough for Tigerhawk to hear...*

" Meet Iris."
